  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Tibial tray fixation FEA credibility assessment (NC-4 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite element analysis of primary tibial tray fixation in total knee arthroplasty under physiological loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict interfacial micromotion at the bone-implant interface for a Class II orthopaedic device at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and Latin hypercube sensitivity analysis are documented. Decision: Accepted.",
